"24:53:14" : {s: 24, a: 53, w: 14, r: "اله", t: "ٱللَّهَ", l: "ٱللَّه", lc: 2811, tl: "l-laha", lb: "আল্লাহ",e: "Allah", b: "আল্লাহকে", i: "Allah", f: 592, rm: "to serve, worship or adore; to protect, grant refuge, preserve save, rescue, liberate; object of worship ie God; (ا-ل-ل-ه) God, the one true God applied as a proper name denoting the true god, comprising all the excellent divine names; a unity comprising all the essences of existing things."},
"24:53:15" : {s: 24, a: 53, w: 15, r: "خبر", t: "خَبِيرٌۢ", l: "خَبِير", lc: 45, tl: "khabīrun", lb: "সব জানেন",e: "(is) All-Aware", b: "সবিশেষ অবহিত", i: "Maha Mengetahui", f: 23, rm: "To know/possess, have knowledge of a thing, to know a thing with respect to its internal or real state, informed/acquainted."},
